Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:22:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1100)\bord0\pos(425,370)\blur1\t(9300,10000,\rnd17\blur5)\t(10000,11000,\rnd30)}第11话\N恐怖·NO·RYO大会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西园同学总是远望着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树想把西园拉入Little Busters吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 让她成为我们的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务开始!
